               <msContents>
                  <summary>
                     <p>I) ዳዊት, Psalter (fols. <locus from="5r" to="170ra"/>)I-<locus target="#1"/>) መዝሙረ፡ዳዊት“Psalms of  David” (fols. <locus from="5r" to="129v"/>) I-<locus target="#2"/>) መኃልየ፡ነቢያት “The Canticles of the Prophets” (fols. <locus from="130r" to="143r"/>) I-<locus target="#3"/>) መኃልየ፡መኃልይ፡ዝውእቱ፡ዘሰሎሞን“Song of Songs of Solomon” (fols. <locus from="143v" to="151r"/>) I-<locus target="#4"/>) ውዳሴ፡ማርያም“The Praise of Mary” (fols. <locus from="151va" to="164ra"/>)</p>
                     <p>I-<locus target="#5"/>) አንቀጸ፡ብርሃን“Gate of Light”(fols. <locus from="164rb" to="170ra"/>) </p>
                     
                     
                     
                  </summary>
                
               </msContents>
