                  <handDesc>
                     <handNote xml:id="h1" script="Ethiopic">Second half of the 19th – early 20th-century script;  Trained, careful hand. <note>
                           <p>Unknown</p>
                           
                        </note>
                        <note>
                           <p>- In order to accommodate longer text lines, the scribe employed compressed script on many folios; and runovers frequently marked with red and/or black lines. </p>
                        </note>
